OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy at first with patchy rain,
OL,7,Fotherwise a dry evening with some late
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Largely clear through
OL,9,Fearly hours but becoming cloudy with
OL,10,Fsome rain later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSome early brightness across
OL,13,Fthe south, otherwise cloudy with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,15,Fpersistent across western parts. The
OL,16,Frain turns more showery later with a
OL,17,Frisk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
