OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,6,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,7,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,8,FMainly dry and bright Monday with
OL,9,Fsunny spells, but cloudier Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
